<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exchange-n">exchange <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ɪks'tʃeɪndʒ/    美 /ɪks'tʃeɪndʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>交换；交流：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>exchange student</strong> 
交换生</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We must promote an <strong>exchange of ideas</strong> and <strong>information</strong>. 
我们必须促进思想和信息的交流。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Would you like my old TV <strong>in exchange for</strong> this camera?
用我的旧电视机换这部照相机，你愿意吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(商品的) 调换：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The store's policy is not to allow returns or exchanges.
这家商店的规定是商品概不退换。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(货币的) 兑换：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>foreign exchange</strong> 
外汇</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>an exchange rate</strong>
汇率</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>交易所：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>New York Stock Exchange 
纽约证券交易所</p></div></div>